# EXCEPTION: the live Supplier Master file is a required runtime asset (fetched by the app
# itself on load, see CLAUDE.md §4) — must be deployed alongside index.html, not excluded.
# Filename must match SUPPLIER_MASTER_FILENAME in index.html exactly — currently
# "supplier_item_master.xlsx" (renamed from "supplier_master.xlsx" at the user's request).
!supplier_item_master.xlsx

